Take 3: Robust PCA from rrcov()

# Robust PCA
rob_pca <- PcaHubert(all_dfm)
# First 2 components account for 65% of variance
print(rob_pca)
## Call:
## PcaHubert(x = all_dfm)

Run MCMC
